formulas.name: ANZARDSAMPLEProductionMethod
formulas.expression: IF( ISPICKVAL({!SemenSample.Sample_Production_Method__c}, "Ejaculate") || ISPICKVAL({!SemenSample.Sample_Production_Method__c}, "Ejaculate with Frozen Backup") || ISPICKVAL({!SemenSample.Sample_Production_Method__c}, "Ejaculate with Frequent Ejaculations Prior") || ISPICKVAL({!SemenSample.Sample_Production_Method__c}, "Retrograde"), "e", IF( ISPICKVAL({!SemenSample.Sample_Production_Method__c}, "Aspirate"), "t", IF( ISPICKVAL({!SemenSample.Sample_Production_Method__c}, "Open Biopsy"), "p", "u" ) ) )

formulas.name: FinalCount
formulas.expression: IF(ISBLANK({!Manual_Prep_Final_Count_ICSI}), (({!Count_1} + {!Count_2}) / {!SemenSample.Rows_Counts__c}) * IF({!Count_Dilution_Pick} = "1:2", 0.1, IF({!Count_Dilution_Pick} = "1:5", 0.25, IF({!Count_Dilution_Pick} = "1:10", 0.5, IF({!Count_Dilution_Pick} = "1:20", 1, IF({!Count_Dilution_Pick} = "1:50", 2.5, 0))))), VALUE({!Manual_Prep_Final_Count_ICSI}))

formulas.name: InseminationTextFormula
formulas.expression: IF(AND(ISBLANK({!SemenSample.Prep_Final_Motility_Text__c}), NOT(ISNUMBER({!SemenSample.Prep_Final_Motility_Text__c}))), "Final Motility is not a Value and therefore cannot be calculated", IF(ISNUMBER({!SemenSample.Prep_Final_Motility_Text__c}), TEXT(ROUND(10000/{!FinalCount}/VALUE({!SemenSample.Prep_Final_Motility_Text__c}),2)), "Final Motility is not a Value and therefore cannot be calculated"))
